The paper discusses the design of data management systems for web applications, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also proposes an ontology-based approach for data integration, which involves reasoning and retrieval of information, indicating the relevance of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of distributed systems, which could be related to deep learning (cs.DL) and software engineering (cs.SE) sub-categories.
